y), UNT at the CHEC brings the power of a UNT education to you. Learn more chec.unt.edu   Contact us UNT at CHEC Phone: 972-599-3126 Email: Myra.Hafer@unt.edu Visit us UNT at CHEC 3452 Spur 399 McKinney, TX 75069 Summer 2017 course offerings Undergraduate Management MGMT 3330 Communicating in Business MGMT 3720 Organizational Behavior Marketing & Logistics MKTG 4120 Consumer Behavior MKTG 3010 Professional Selling MKTG 3830 Operations Management Fall 2017 course offerings Undergraduate BAAS PACS 3000 Civic Engagement PACS 3020 Inquiry and Discovery PACS 4000 Mediation PACS 4010 Family Mediation PACS 4050 Negotiation Management MGMT 3330 Communicating in Business MGMT 3720 Organizational Behavior MGMT 3860 Human Resource Management MGMT 3880 Business Ethics & Social Responsibility Marketing & Logistics MKTG 3010 Professional Selling MKTG 3650 Foundations of Marketing Practice LSCM 3960 Logistics & Supply Chain Management Take the next step Freshmen Transfers Grad students Online offerings Contact us Top Required Links Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info Main Menu Home Admissions Academics Student Life About UNT Research Athletics Giving University Links MyUNT EagleConnect Blackboard People & Departments Calendar UNT Map Jobs at UNT Colleges & Schools Specifically for Current Students Faculty & Staff Alumni & Friends Parents & Family Community Emails Graduate Admissions Freshman Admissions Transfer Admissions International Admissions     Find UNT on Google Maps 1155 Union Circle #311277 Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information   940-565-2000   800-RELAY TX   Technical Issues Call us Email Us UNT Map Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links ©2017 University of North Texas 